# Notarization credentials. Copy to `electron-builder.env` (gitignored) and fill in.
# electron-builder auto-loads `electron-builder.env` from the project root at build
# time — no `export` needed. Real shell env vars take precedence over this file.
# `${HOME}` is expanded (dotenv-expand); a literal `~` is NOT, so use ${HOME}.

# App Store Connect API key (recommended). Create at appstoreconnect.apple.com →
# Users and Access → Integrations → App Store Connect API (Developer role).
APPLE_API_KEY=${HOME}/.appstoreconnect/private/AuthKey_XXXXXXXXXX.p8
APPLE_API_KEY_ID=XXXXXXXXXX
APPLE_API_ISSUER=xxxxxxxx-xxxx-xxxx-xxxx-xxxxxxxxxxxx

# Alternative to the API key: Apple ID + app-specific password (appleid.apple.com).
# APPLE_ID=you@example.com
# APPLE_APP_SPECIFIC_PASSWORD=xxxx-xxxx-xxxx-xxxx
# APPLE_TEAM_ID=NN7378S6P5
